Melon is an experimental fiber M:N library implementation.

It should be portable, but it's developped and tested on Linux ATM.

Cheers


Dependencies
~~~~~~~~~~~~

 - c99 (gcc or clang)
 - pthreads
 - linux/epoll
 - *bsd/kqueue [not implemented yet]
 - solaris,windows/iocp [not implemented yet]
 - cmake

